   SubscriptBox["\[DoubleStruckCapitalQ]", "p"], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"8840b5d6-6bc1-4ea7-a78d-a487056bd436"],
 ":\nP-adic Expansions, Hensel\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Lemma, and \n\
