Cell["\<\
These numbers are racing toward infinity. And yet, in a precise mathematical \
sense, they are converging \[LongDash] to negative one.
Check: every one of them, plus 1, is divisible by the highest power of 3 \
available:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.981585565629443*^9, 3.981585572133621*^9}, {
  3.9815856063431664`*^9, 
  3.981585609585895*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"59a5a2cb-5f9c-49e4-8dbc-\
205be40805cd"],

