Cell["\<\
This results in an eventually periodic expansion with the only a single digit \
as a non-repeating part. Further we can use the following relationships for \
its computation\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.884139063913213*^9, 3.8841391310876913`*^9}, {
   3.8841394034329443`*^9, 3.884139436653371*^9}, {3.884139488135891*^9, 
