  3.8843910701111917`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c36faf5b-c81d-40db-b74c-\
5225fc559795"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "is purely periodic. This is an ever increasing positive series, so there \
must be one index ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"n", "<", "k"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b0089f51-e8d8-4cd0-99b5-6952de7278c0"],
 " and m for which"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8841733906746683`*^9, 3.8841734582038593`*^9}, {
   3.884212928676064*^9, 3.884212966850099*^9}, {3.884386471084116*^9, 
