Cell["\<\
Next, the general topic of negation, we can build on case 2b where we have a \
non-zero & non-repeating part:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8841733906746683`*^9, 3.8841734582038593`*^9}, {
   3.884212928676064*^9, 3.884212966850099*^9}, {3.884385615658572*^9, 
